PrecisAmendments to the LIFE SAVING EQUIPMENT REGULATIONS which will require that all new ships be fitted with modern life-saving equipment, that when a ship's equipment is upgraded it be replaced with the same modern equipment required on new vessels, and that all classes of ships be fitted with enough lifeboats to accommodate its full complement of passengers and crew.
